Name: IRQ_CLEAR
Description:
Write a '1' to this field to clear a timer interrupt request. If
the timer crosses zero at the same time as the write, the
clear operation will fail; interrupt request will remain
asserted. This bit self-clears.

Name: RELOAD
Description:
Write a '1' to this field to (re)load the timer with the timeout
value. This bit self-clears.
